{
  "stem": "521.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, we had then-- we could take some tree trunks home-- not the whole ones, just pieces-- which we were supposed to cut up, and there was a stove which we could burn the tree trunks or whatever would we could get.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And but many times, we were so tired that we just went to sleep and covered myself in my [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sleeping bag and went to sleep immediately.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went to sleep around 7 o'clock or 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at 6 o'clock, we got up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the night was so short that we didn't realize that the night was gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no-- we could escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Escape where?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was if-- the only place we could escape was going back to our parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if we tried to do that, they would have come and got us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There weren't people who were escaping, even after when our life was depending on it, very few people escaped because if they were found, they were shot dead right there and then.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was not much of a help.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, I have to tell you that at that time when we had enough tree trunks on-- on top of a mountain, we were digging holes-- squares.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's as big into the ground as a room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, when it was done properly, we-- we have put in the tree trunks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we lined it from inside, and at the bottom, and at the top.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, this was supposed to be a-- a bunker, a fortification, if and when the Russians are going to come.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
